Title: The YouTube Killer: The Strange Case of Andrew Blaze
Description:
In the early hours of the 8th of June, 2017, Randy Stair, aka. YouTube creator Andrew Blaze, shot and killed 3 of his co-workers before turning his gun on himself. For months, Stair had discussed his plans openly on his various YouTube channels, and yet no one stopped him. This is the tragic story about how he'd cried out for help for years, and received only silence in return.
